description: Use Daily Specials to get the daily specials menu from restaurants that use the emenuPlus restaurant ecommerce system. Specific restaurant locations may be queried by location address.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Daily Specials for Cafe Metro
Alexa, ask Daily Specials for Cafe Metro at 14 East 42nd Street
Alexa, tell Daily Specials to give me Cafe Metro
name: Daily Specials
shortDescription: Get daily specials menu for restaurants using the emenuPlus system.
